hwMeta.bodyText:
If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        write_ptr(0),
        read_ptr0(0),
        looped0(0)
    ).Else(
        write_ptr(write_ptr_next),
        read_ptr0(read_ptr0_next),
        looped0(looped0_next)
    )
)

If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        wWordCntr(0),
        wErrFlag(0),
        lastReqDispatched(1)
    ).Else(
        wWordCntr(wWordCntr_next),
        wErrFlag(wErrFlag_next),
        lastReqDispatched(lastReqDispatched_next)
    )
)

If(lastReqDispatched._eq(1),
    id(driver_req_id),
    a_addr(driver_req_addr),
    If(driver_req_len > 255,
        a_len(255)
    ).Else(
        a_len(sig_0)
    ),
    req_idBackup_next(driver_req_id),
    addrBackup_next((driver_req_addr._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32, signed=False)) + 2048)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32))),
    lenDebth_next((driver_req_len._reinterpret_cast(Bits(9, signed=False)) - 256)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(9))),
    If((sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_rd & a_ready & driver_req_vld)._eq(1),
        If(driver_req_len > 255,
            lastReqDispatched_next(0)
        ).Else(
            lastReqDispatched_next(1)
        )
    ).Else(
        lastReqDispatched_next(lastReqDispatched)
    ),
    driver_req_rd(a_ready & sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_rd),
    a_valid(driver_req_vld & sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_rd & ~wErrFlag),
    sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_vld(driver_req_vld & a_ready)
).Else(
    id(req_idBackup),
    a_addr(addrBackup),
    If(lenDebth > 255,
        a_len(255)
    ).Else(
        a_len(sig_1)
    ),
    a_valid(sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_rd & ~wErrFlag),
    sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_vld(a_ready),
    driver_req_rd(0),
    If((sig_writeInfoFifo_dataIn_rd & a_ready)._eq(1),
        addrBackup_next((addrBackup._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32, signed=False)) + 2048)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32))),
        lenDebth_next((lenDebth._reinterpret_cast(Bits(9, signed=False)) - 256)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(9))),
        If(lenDebth <= 255,
            lastReqDispatched_next(1)
        ).Else(
            lastReqDispatched_next(lastReqDispatched)
        )
    ).Else(
        addrBackup_next(addrBackup),
        lastReqDispatched_next(lastReqDispatched),
        lenDebth_next(lenDebth)
    ),
    req_idBackup_next(req_idBackup)
)

If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        write_ptr(0),
        read_ptr0(0),
        looped0(0)
    ).Else(
        write_ptr(write_ptr_next),
        read_ptr0(read_ptr0_next),
        looped0(looped0_next)
    )
)
